{"tid":1653130,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"如果割頸手足都話係中共特務 當condom 我都無心抗爭落去","createTime":"2019-10-14T03:02:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T07:17:36.000Z","uid":118228,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"69da83e68733ee4b7936af3683ecf4704fcb1e59","tid":1653130,"uid":118228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T03:02:29.000Z","msg":"我自問唔夠膽 但我絕對支持 亦絕對唔會當佢係鬼<br />\n<br />\n但我見到個中共特務post 有成千幾正評 我睇到真係好灰心<br />\n<br />\n好多嘢想講 例如法案緊要 但手足更重要 例如唔好再捉鬼 講真連登/fb網上捉鬼次次都捉錯哂 例如唔好再將勇武行為spin去黑警/中共臥底所做 因為對家根本無人信 但自己人就呃埋自己<br />\n<br />\n但我真係好攰 而加仲要病緊 唔想打太多字 次次行動我都出哂咁滯 我唔敢企最前 但我都係三四排 最前線唔真係掉頭跑我都唔走 <br />\n<br />\n呢d我都覺得值得 不過呢d post 呢d言論 呢d諗法 我反而覺得最大打擊 希望同路人唔好再自作聰明 唔好再呃自己 <br />\n<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 核爆都唔割"},{"pid":"4b8c8ea2f7e5c29f307e8c0aa532a01550bd530c","tid":1653130,"uid":258068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T03:12:46.000Z","msg":"[前線][文宣入]用黑警借車反咬政府一口<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1652306\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1652306</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n幫推<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我地有能力反分化政府！</span></span><br />\n推呀！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">入尼睇下唔勇武我地可以點做</span>"},{"pid":"7c9abfb0a17a7b697916c61eea348dbdec1bb2da","tid":1653130,"uid":260023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:17:36.000Z","msg":"幫我推一下<br />\n<br />\n一